<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>279</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Dam sungin I Tanpau vangin,
 Nunnuom in kikhawm mah leu hing;
 Kapin I kikhen kit sek ui,
 Aw ka ngai khenlohna gam nuom.

[V2]
 Hukdampa vangkhuo sat thakah,
 Simlei a gibang kikhen te;
 Kumsawt Lalchutphah kimvel in,
 Aw bangtik leh I kikhawm dem ?

[V3]
 2. Ngo bang a lang Kalvari ah,
 Galdawt leng khenlohna gam chu;
 Nga bang lenna tang dang mahleh
 Ginnan laituol lengkhawm hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Theibang lo leng Lalpa sakmin,
 Thawmhau liengvai ei nem dingin
 Naubang ei nem ding a um puoi
 Sam tui bang tawm simlei nunnawp.

[V5]
 4. Nuoi simlei ahin le Ama'n
 A lungsietna tha lim nuoiah
 Nunnawp laituol lengkhawm kit di'n
 Chang bang damin ei pui khawm ding.</lyrics>
<title>Khen Lohna Gam Ka Ngai</title>
</song>